Shredface Collection
Is a Unique hand-drawn self-portrait collection. Coming from a forgotten life, I named myself Shredface, wandering around the world. Trying to remember who I was. I've had many lives on this adventure, but none seem to answer this question, where my journey is taking me next? Will I find out who I am?...

Published November 2021
